metadata.name: E'arth #1
metadata.description:
A 1/1 handmade artwork/NFT from YthsArt. Made with acrylic, sand and stones on a canvas 40x50cm.

Collection is inspired by the Earth seen from the space.

Every first buyer of the NFT has the right to redeem the original artwork. Shipping (all over the world) will be included in the price.

For shipping details send an email after buying to:
ythsart@gmail.com
